Name: aditi_fast_food
Summary: [{'summary_text': "Amar Juice Centre is located near Andheri Station . It's a good place to have some quick bites. It is a nice place to visit if you are looking for a quick bite . The food is very good and the ambience is good ."}]

Summary: [{'summary_text': "I had huge expectations from Prithvi cafe because of its name . Taste was bad... I felt like they gave me yesterday's remaining, reheated bhaji . Name: grandmama's_cafe
Summary: [{'summary_text': "Grandmama's Cafe Juhu has been revamped by the talented Gauri Khan . The menu has undergone a massive overhaul over the years . It's an amazing and new fresh look for all ages ."}]

Name: alfredo's
Summary: [{'summary_text': 'The restaurant is a cool place to go out and have a meal with friends and family . It has a vibrant atmosphere located close to juhu beach. The staff is very rude and arrogant, they dint even have proper uniforms to wear, beware of Bhim and the other guy who serves the outside area .'}]

Name: candies
Summary: [{'summary_text': "This place is a great place for non-vegetarians as it offers a wide variety of food over vegetarian options . Name: the_house_of_pasta
Summary: [{'summary_text': 'The House of Pasta is a pure veg cafe with over 20 mouth-watering pasta varieties starting at just Rs. 220 . The pasta was rich of sauce and it was properly tossed to give a sound taste of each ingredient added to it .'}]

Name: pasta_hub
Summary: [{'summary_text': "Pasta hub is located at Mahavir Nagar Kandivali West Mumbai . It's having large Varieties of Pizza, Pasta, Nachos, Garlic bread and many more items . We ordered Classic veg Pizza  Maharaja Pasta  would rate 3.5 stars ."}]
